(Why Role is set automatically: normal registration should never allow a user to choose Admin in JSON.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Login logic:) Tj
T*
(  if user does not exist OR password does not match:) Tj
T*
(      throw Invalid username or password) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Why the message is general: attackers should not know whether the username or password was wrong.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Database migration for task 034:) Tj
T*
(  AddUserPasswordHash adds PasswordHash to Users table.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Command:) Tj
T*
(  dotnet ef database update --project EfcDataAccess --startup-project WebAPI) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If migration is not applied, POST /Users can return 500 because the database is missing PasswordHash.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Task 035 - JWT Authorization) Tj
T*
(Goal: after login, the user receives a token. Todo endpoints require that token.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Login response DTO:) Tj
T*
(  Token) Tj
T*
(  User) Tj
T*
(  ExpiresAtUtc) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Why: The frontend or Swagger needs the token for later protected requests.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(JWT claims added:) Tj
T*
(  ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier = user.Id) Tj
T*
(  ClaimTypes.Name = user.UserName) Tj
T*
(  ClaimTypes.Role = user.Role) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Meaning:) Tj
T*
(  NameIdentifier tells the backend the logged-in user id.) Tj
T*
(  Name tells the backend the username.) Tj
T*
(  Role tells the backend whether the user is User or Admin.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(JWT validation in Program.cs checks:) Tj
T*
(  - issuer) Tj
T*
(  - audience) Tj
T*
(  - lifetime) Tj
T*
(  - signing key) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Middleware order:) Tj
T*
(  app.UseAuthentication\(\);) Tj
T*
ET
