(4. Copy the token from the login response.) Tj
T*
(5. Click Authorize in Swagger.) Tj
T*
(6. Paste Bearer {token}.) Tj
T*
(7. Call Todo endpoints.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. Common Errors) Tj
T*
(500 when creating user: database is missing PasswordHash or Role. Run dotnet ef database update.) Tj
T*
(No Authorize button: Swagger Bearer setup is missing or WebAPI was not restarted.) Tj
T*
(401 Unauthorized: missing, expired, or invalid token. Login again and paste Bearer token.) Tj
T*
(404 for existing todo: the todo may belong to another user. Use owner token or Admin token.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. Final Mental Model) Tj
T*
(Register: username + password -> hash password -> save UserName, PasswordHash, Role) Tj
T*
(Login: username + password -> verify hash -> return JWT) Tj
T*
(Todo request: frontend sends JWT -> backend validates token -> backend reads user id and role -> allows or blocks action) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
